The Hawkswood Advantage
 We are confident in our abilities. With over 25 years of construction and building, we've developed the quality customers come to expect. Professionalism, Integrity, Honesty are the first qualities Hawkswood brings to our projects. Visit our reviews and customer referrals. As a complete design and build general contracting firm, we know what needs to be done and how to do it right the first time. Peterborough, Kawartha Lakes, Trent Hills, Hastings, Northumberland and Quinte West areas have been our playground for the past 15 years. We know the people, we are the people. Call us today to discuss your next project and see how we can serve you.
